<i>The sea cures it all?</i>

25:02.752 --> 25:04.670
<i>Kannalab was born by the sea.</i>

25:11.219 --> 25:13.387
<i>And we hadn't hung out
in a long time.</i>

25:13.429 --> 25:14.513
<i>Where?</i>

25:15.473 --> 25:17.642
<i>Here, in Bogotá.</i>

25:56.555 --> 26:03.437
WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?

26:12.863 --> 26:14.740
WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?

27:03.664 --> 27:04.498
What's up?

27:05.541 --> 27:07.585
Shit, it's freezing!

27:07.626 --> 27:09.670
That must be why they call
this city The Freezer.

27:09.712 --> 27:10.629
Oh, yes.

27:12.757 --> 27:14.133
So... How's the
marijuana life going?

27:15.468 --> 27:17.887
It's going.
You wanna get a drink?

27:18.679 --> 27:20.264
No. I don't feel like it.

27:20.306 --> 27:21.766
Not even a coffee?

27:21.807 --> 27:24.518
No, let's hang some other time.
I have a lot to do.

27:25.144 --> 27:26.062
All right.

27:32.610 --> 27:33.736
You know what, kid?

27:34.945 --> 27:37.448
I'm going to leave so
people don't think

27:37.490 --> 27:39.033
I'm trying to mug you in here.

27:39.075 --> 27:40.493
- I'll see you in a month.
- Hey.

27:41.202 --> 27:42.828
How's the man doing?

27:44.663 --> 27:46.791
I've told you not to ask about him
many times.

27:48.542 --> 27:51.295
You're doing more than enough,
believe me.

27:54.340 --> 27:55.174
Goodbye.

28:11.607 --> 28:13.025
- Can I help you?
- No.

28:17.196 --> 28:18.155
I'll be late.

30:52.059 --> 30:53.227
You're a little early but--

30:53.269 --> 30:55.771
- I'm sorry!
- No, Samantha, don't say that.

30:55.813 --> 30:56.939
We're all set for you,

30:56.981 --> 30:58.190
- we have some snacks.
- So nice, thanks.

30:58.232 --> 30:59.942
Daniel, so nice, thank you.

30:59.984 --> 31:01.735
Oh, the apartment is amazing!

31:01.777 --> 31:03.153
Thank you!

31:03.195 --> 31:04.530
Make yourself at home, welcome.

31:04.572 --> 31:05.531
Samantha?

31:05.573 --> 31:06.615
Hi, Lucas.

31:06.657 --> 31:08.617
- What's up?
- It's really beautiful.

31:09.201 --> 31:10.160
Daniel.

31:10.202 --> 31:11.453
Wine, anyone? I'm
opening a Malbec,

31:11.495 --> 31:12.830
my favorite. If you want,

31:12.871 --> 31:13.956
- we can try this one after.
- I want some.

31:13.998 --> 31:15.040
- Right away.
- Thanks!

31:15.082 --> 31:16.667
Yes, of course.

31:16.709 --> 31:19.545
You wouldn't have let me invite them
if I told you, so...

31:20.796 --> 31:23.257
You know how tense
things are with her.

31:23.299 --> 31:25.342
That's precisely why.

31:25.384 --> 31:30.514
We can smooth things out and you
will become boss of the year.

32:12.931 --> 32:14.933
What are you doing here,
brother?

32:20.356 --> 32:22.691
Do you know what could happen
if these people

32:22.733 --> 32:24.610
find out you're out here?

32:25.986 --> 32:27.404
Kid...

32:27.446 --> 32:28.864
don't be a dumbass.

32:29.907 --> 32:31.742
Get out of here.

32:31.784 --> 32:33.035
Go live your life.

32:34.870 --> 32:35.704
Go.

33:12.157 --> 33:13.492
No, thank you.

33:17.579 --> 33:19.289
Been waiting all day
for this moment.

33:20.708 --> 33:22.918
How so? You can still smoke
during the day, right?

33:25.295 --> 33:27.214
He always says I smell
like cigarettes.

33:29.633 --> 33:31.218
Unbelievable.

33:31.260 --> 33:33.762
No matter what you do, you still
have to ask for permission.

33:35.556 --> 33:39.059
I imagine that choosing to be
independent wasn't an easy decision.

33:40.436 --> 33:42.146
It never is.

33:46.024 --> 33:48.152
It must not be easy, either...

33:48.193 --> 33:51.029
to lose a position
that you're the best fit for.

33:53.490 --> 33:54.867
Don't let your husband hear you.

33:57.202 --> 34:00.539
He knows that in a couple of years
you'll be president of the company.

34:04.042 --> 34:06.003
I don't know why I feel like...

34:06.044 --> 34:08.672
all this flattery should come
with the dessert,

34:08.714 --> 34:10.466
and we're still not there yet.

34:10.507 --> 34:14.386
All I've said so far is true.

34:14.428 --> 34:16.430
Then we can keep talking inside.

34:26.398 --> 34:27.399
Ilana Frank.

34:27.441 --> 34:28.859
What about her?

34:28.901 --> 34:31.069
You have a business relationship
with her company, right?

34:31.111 --> 34:33.864
- Do you need a recommendation?
- I need her personal info.

34:36.575 --> 34:37.534
I can't believe it.

34:38.744 --> 34:40.913
Did you bad-mouth Lucas
to get a contact?

34:40.954 --> 34:43.749
I didn't bad-mouth my husband.
I'm just speaking nicely of you.

34:43.791 --> 34:45.667
I'm just not the type of woman

34:45.709 --> 34:48.086
who does charity
in exchange for flattery.

34:50.464 --> 34:52.299
We could talk money, then.

35:00.808 --> 35:03.143
I'm not a slut who sells herself
for money, either.

35:06.605 --> 35:08.065
The food was very nice.

35:32.631 --> 35:33.507
Mom!

35:34.049 --> 35:35.092
Mom!

35:35.592 --> 35:36.718
Mom!

35:55.237 --> 35:56.530
We had a nice time today.

35:59.157 --> 36:01.243
What a good idea to
invite Samantha.

36:02.703 --> 36:03.579
Yes.

36:03.620 --> 36:05.122
You know what I was thinking?

36:06.373 --> 36:08.834
Why don't we go to a
fertility doctor?

36:10.043 --> 36:10.794
You think?

36:12.087 --> 36:15.465
Why force things?
Let's go with the flow, no?

36:15.507 --> 36:18.552
- I agree, go with the flow.
- Right.

36:18.594 --> 36:21.054
But we've tried for a long time,

36:21.096 --> 36:22.639
and nothing happens.

36:22.681 --> 36:25.767
And, honestly, I'm worried
that there's a problem.

36:27.019 --> 36:30.564
What problem?
We're both in perfect shape.

36:30.606 --> 36:32.149
Nothing's wrong.

36:32.190 --> 36:34.026
I know, I'm sure there's
nothing wrong.

36:34.067 --> 36:38.155
It doesn't hurt to hear
an expert's opinion, either.

36:40.032 --> 36:41.325
Really?

36:45.037 --> 36:46.121
Okay.

36:46.163 --> 36:47.623
If it'll put you at ease...

36:48.832 --> 36:50.876
All right. Let's make
an appointment.

36:54.421 --> 36:55.839
We're a great team.

37:04.473 --> 37:05.265
What happened to her?

37:06.308 --> 37:08.185
She suffered liver
failure which,

37:08.226 --> 37:10.312
combined with the wine,
made her pass out.

37:10.354 --> 37:12.606
Has her cancer metastasized?

37:12.648 --> 37:16.318
You know, chemotherapy
is poison attacking live cells.

37:16.360 --> 37:18.403
Your mom suspended
the treatment,

37:18.445 --> 37:21.698
so her body didn't get
enough medicine

37:21.740 --> 37:24.117
to protect her vital organs.

37:24.159 --> 37:27.287
Listen, Felix. Eva needs to resume
her treatment as soon as possible.

37:28.872 --> 37:31.833
Today we were lucky to save her,
but tomorrow we don't know.

38:15.836 --> 38:19.798
THANK YOU.

38:24.845 --> 38:30.392
BE CAREFUL WITH HER.

38:35.272 --> 38:36.356
What's so urgent?

38:39.067 --> 38:40.902
How much would you pay
for the weed?

38:48.618 --> 38:51.580
Miss, Lola. It's ready. Look.

38:52.456 --> 38:53.749
This was the whole problem.

38:54.875 --> 38:56.918
It got tangled and so
did the food.

38:56.960 --> 38:58.670
It was that fucking necklace.

39:00.630 --> 39:01.548
Do you like it?

39:04.092 --> 39:05.427
Take it.

39:05.469 --> 39:06.678
<i>With your permission.</i>

39:06.720 --> 39:07.929
Thanks.
